{"tid":895333,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華夢中情人選舉冠軍43歲譚筠怡繼續惹火 網上晒泳照派福利!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2018-11-09T06:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T10:31:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"19b1a3c5c0568e9648f92771bd00d9e869d4d1a7","tid":895333,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"又係失蹤人口呀！邊個記得譚筠怡（Gwennie）請舉手！身材索爆嘅Gwennie，當年只有16歲，為見偶像劉德華，o氹掂一直覺得娛樂圈係大染缸嘅父親，俾佢參加「劉德華夢中情人選舉」，結果佢仲攞埋個冠軍，繼而晉身娛樂圈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541594253_1f46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541594253_1f46.jpg&h=a1a2f90e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早前參加萬聖節派對扮到鬼火咁靚。<br />\n<br />\n不過，現年43歲嘅Gwennie，05年已經離開咗香港娛樂圈去從商。雖然喺美國定居，但Gwennie久唔久都會返香港探屋企人，而喺美國就仍然有參與電影同模特兒工作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541594257_76c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541594257_76c5.jpg&h=a806f4cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成日都同愛犬影合照。<br />\n<br />\n人唔喺香港啫，想知Gwennie變成點，上網都可以睇到嘅，可見今次投注第128期六合彩時，如不兼顧此類旺門分子或較蝕底。事關佢不時都會喺社交網貼下靚相，新鮮滾熱辣嘅係一張三點式泳照，身型fit到漏嘅佢，身材同樣貌都keep得相當好，甚至比早年更加fit，完全唔似43歲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541594255_db15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541594255_db15.jpg&h=c55db563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嘩嘩嘩，邊忽似43歲先？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541594253_b672.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541594253_b672.jpg&h=442df65c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上次上載泳照已經係一年前。<br />\n<br />\nGwennie拍過電視劇，也拍過電影，00年仲同前港姐梁珮瑚細佬梁焯滿，合作拍咗部三級片《獸性新人類》，片中兩人有唔少火辣肉博場面，佢嘅演出相當大膽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181107/large/1541594253_c513.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181107%2Flarge%2F1541594253_c513.jpg&h=d124eb8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚筠怡咁多年都係咁索。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181109/large/1541693472_10b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181109%2Flarge%2F1541693472_10b0.jpg&h=6ac68686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周六有馬跑，周日才開六合彩。<br />\n<br />\n可惜博到盡，加埋樣靚身材正，都未有為Gwennie事業帶來起色，反而負面新聞多多，05年更捲入女藝人「掘金」風波，Gwennie否認傳聞後更轉戰商場，除了在澳門開餐廳，又進軍珠寶界成立自家品牌，她又努力增值自己，修讀珠寶鑑證及設計課程，11年更贏得不少國際級珠寶設計大獎，叫做幫自己爭番口氣。"},{"pid":"b9d1feab1fb97acb0207324181a6c707da1ecec4","tid":895333,"uid":2795,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"俾肥屍屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c0b1d98aec845eb8b397a45db49cd9e1d38f7b","tid":895333,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"個六合彩係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae8e4d68eb3c527bfc1bc5479a9b8fff9903917","tid":895333,"uid":30640,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"21c0b1d98aec845eb8b397a45db49cd9e1d38f7b","tid":895333,"uid":14766,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"個六合彩係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"無啦啦有句第128期六合彩咩事"},{"pid":"2857a40237fbc260f4897d78e6a59135e625064b","tid":895333,"uid":65956,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"9ae8e4d68eb3c527bfc1bc5479a9b8fff9903917","tid":895333,"uid":30640,"like":4,"dislik